owlSpeak.engine

Class MasterSlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • owlSpeak.engine.MasterSlot

  • public class MasterSlot
extends java.lang.Object
    The class that represents all POMDP Slots. Contain all SLot that have been created. It is used to prove if a Slot already exist.
    Author:
    Savina Koleva.
